title: 蓝碳指数评估
description: 基于我国沿海蓝碳生态系统（红树林、盐沼、海草床）的保护与开发场景，运用卫星遥感（Sentinel-2/Landsat）、无人机多光谱监测、物联网传感器及生态社会多源数据，解决监测精度不足、碳汇量化标准缺失、市场价值难实现三大核心问题，基于蓝碳指数精准量化沿海生态系统碳汇能力，驱动碳汇资源市场化转化，实现2030年新增年固碳50万吨、培育30-50亿元蓝碳交易市场的战略目标。

form.text:
Function: Collect information such as keywords, titles, audience, words/brands to avoid, tone, and other details provided by the user.

Variables:
 - keyword：Keywords
 - title：Title, 
 - audience：Audience
 - brands_to_avoid：Words/brands to avoid.

MUST NOT both of keywords and title are blank.
If title is not empty, let LLM help you to generate keywords.

Use user defined keywords to search.
Next, generate a title based on the search result.
Change to DuckDuckGo if you want.

Let LLM to generate keywords to search. 
Based on the search result, the outline of the article will be generated.

The user enters information such as avoid keywords, title, audience, required words/brands, tone, etc. at the start node.

2. Conditional judgment:
Check whether the title is empty, if it is empty, generate the title.

3. Generate titles and keywords:
Generate SEO optimized titles and related keywords based on the entered user keywords.

4. Web search:
Use the generated titles and keywords to conduct a Google search to obtain relevant information.

5. Generate outline and articles:
Generate article outlines, topics, and bodies based on user input information and search results.

6. Template conversion and output:
Combine the beginning of the article and the main body to generate a complete article, and output the result.
